    text: 'I had been struggling with sun spots on my face for years. After 4 treatments, they have almost completely disappeared! Finally, I can go out confidently without makeup.',
    author: 'Katalin',
  },
  {
    text: 'The pigment spots that appeared after pregnancy really bothered me. The Beautyflow team worked wonders – my skin is smooth and radiant again.',
    author: 'Reka',
  },
  {
    text: 'Professional team, impressive results. The treatment was painless, and I saw changes after the very first session.',
    author: 'Zsofia',
  }
