    description: 'We clean and prepare the treatment area. Eyes are protected with safety goggles, and the surrounding skin is treated with a special gel.'
  },
  {
    number: '3.',
    title: 'Nd:YAG Laser Treatment',
    description: 'The laser energy is absorbed specifically by the pigment, breaking it down without damaging the surrounding tissues. The treatment is quick and gentle.'
  },
  {
    number: '4.',
    title: 'Aftercare and Results',
    description: 'The scab on the treated area falls off naturally within 7-10 days. During the regeneration period, the skin should be cared for with a special cream and SPF 50 sunscreen.'
